No. 11-5311 (11A72). Thomas Paul West, Petitioner v. Arizona. 564 U.S. 1053, 131 S. Ct. 3092,

180 L. Ed. 2d 913,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 5021. July 19, 2011.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented *914to Justice Kennedy, and by him referred to the Court, denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Superior Court of Arizona, Pima County, denied.
